data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!  Welcome Home!!  Come see this spacious 4 bedroom/3 bath Deltona home built in 2003 and located on an oversized lot in a cul-de-sac!  Beautiful ceramic decorative tiles throughout the 1969 square foot home.  Super nice interior with split bedroom floor plan and TWO master bedroom ensuites with private bathrooms. The primary master bedroom has an incredible custom bathroom with garden jacuzzi tub, dual sinks and separate wash closet & shower stall. The other three bedrooms are on the other side of the home which offer privacy and a perfect set up for a growing family.  Huge kitchen & Great Room combination with French doors leading out to screened porch.  The kitchen has been renovated and it is the "Heart of the Home". The Great Room is really GREAT with high ceilings and built in shelving & entertainment center. All newer appliances stay and convey with the sale including Samsung washer and dryer located in a separate interior Laundry Room. Backyard has "lifetime" vinyl fencing for security and privacy and rock gardens with Papaya trees to minimize landscaping and lawn care.  The above ground pool can stay & convey if desired.  Come & see this gem nestled in Deltona with very little traffic and quiet living and conveniently located near shopping, restaurants and medical facilities. This could be your new home very soon so call and set up a showing!!!
